# Bubblewrap / Android TWA
# Keystore files must NEVER be committed — they're the app signing identity.
# Lose the keystore = can't ship updates to the same Play Store listing.
# Store them in a password manager and document the location offline.
*.keystore
*.jks
mobile/android-twa/build/
mobile/android-twa/app/build/
mobile/android-twa/.gradle/
mobile/android-twa/local.properties

# Translation routine artefacts (throwaway, not committed)
.claude-translations/

# Ephemeral agent-orchestration coordination state (process, not product)
.orchestration/

.nx/migrate-runs